      "title": "A semantics of python in isabelle/hol",
      "abstract": "A Semantics of Python in Isabelle/HOLJames F. Ranson,Howard J. Hamiltonand Philip W. L. FongTechnical Report CS-2008-04December 2008Copyright c 2008 J. F. Ranson, H. J. Hamilton, P. W. L. FongDepartment of Computer ScienceUniversity of ReginaRegina, Saskatchewan, S4S 0A2CanadaISBN 978-0-7731-0657-4 (print)ISBN 978-0-7731-0658-1 (online)"
